Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:04.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Was it all a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:06.91,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:07.90,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:10.32,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Did you have a bad dream ag-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:11.19,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:18.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Were you just pretending to have a heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:22.20,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Pretending? What does "pretending-"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:23.71,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It means lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:26.50,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It means saying things you don't mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:30.88,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:35.72,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,My job is to be useful to you and make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:38.76,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That's the motivation behind everything I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:44.69,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,When you said you might have a heart, did you mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:50.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Did you say that because you really do think you have a heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:55.78,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:57.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Then here's an order for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:00:59.41,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Stop pretending you have a heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:01.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Stop trying to make me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:06.83,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:12.46,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Why did you lie to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:15.26,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I have already answered that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:17.34,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Do you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.85,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,As you are now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:25.23,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:38.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.43,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm high-spec!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Was it all a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That time, and that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:40.78,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and that time, and that time, and that time, all of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Was it all a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:20.36,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You sure he's okay? Whatever happened, it was serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:23.74,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Yeah... When we found him sprawled out on the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:26.03,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,I thought I was gonna have a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:34.16,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Thanks, you two. I'll ask him what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:35.17,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.17,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.88,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Okay, you can take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.15,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Did you two fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:01.82,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Minamo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.32,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:13.83,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No, I knew all along. She's a Humanoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.58,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,There's no way she could have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:24.30,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She was just scouring her massive stores of data,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.13,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,cross-referencing situations and reactions,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.68,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and picking the optimal solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She laughed when she was supposed to,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,got angry when she was supposed to,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.69,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,faithfully running her programs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.98,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,to manufacture her facial expressions and tailor her words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:45.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's what Humanoids are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.41,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,You know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:02.63,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I think that's no different from what we humans do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.96,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I know I'm like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:09.89,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I look at the other person, think about what I should say to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:14.43,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,and choose my words based on how they look and act.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:18.39,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I don't know what a heart is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:25.36,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Even if you know it's wrong, even if you have nothing to gain,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.95,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,you'll still say or do something stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:38.08,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I think you're right, and she really does have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:43.17,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But I think she's doubting herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:47.80,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,She's nervous about having a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:53.60,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:56.35,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Sorry. I figured you were cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.89,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Should I have let it cool a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,This is just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:12.91,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:17.41,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I went to check on Atri-chan, and she was doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.50,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,She said she'd go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.62,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:27.05,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I'll tell everyone you're out with a cold, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.34,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.13,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:34.18,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,My students need someone to teach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.30,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:40.89,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I can't exactly avoid Atri forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:46.77,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I had a feeling you'd say that. I brought your uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.82,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,Sure won't stop raining, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.74,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:53.95,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:56.20,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Natsuki-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:58.95,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.83,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Where's Atrin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.96,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Is she not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.17,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,She said she'd come...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.26,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.43,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,No return address.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:19.31,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,It's a report on the recall of Yamasaki Factory's fourth-generation models.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.60,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yamasaki Factory...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.98,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,So it's about Atri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:29.78,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Yeah. This probably came from someone who knows she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Rampage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:37.28,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,"In defiance of its user's orders, the unit in question infiltrated a school
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.87,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,and severely injured its students."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:40.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:44.41,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I don't know if she really was "the unit in question."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:49.55,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,But they only ever sold a grand total of 58 of her model.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.13,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Once they recalled them all,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:57.18,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,just one, "the unit in question," broke out and went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:01.47,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,But Yamasaki Factory covered that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.68,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the hubbub surrounding the recall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.77,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,soured demand for Humanoids, and the company went under.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.31,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,And so they never recovered the missing unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And that unit was Atri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.86,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,There's no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.11,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,This report could be completely made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:21.91,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,But I'm responsible for these kids' safety, so I have to err on the side of caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:29.25,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,So I told her, "I'm sorry, but I can't let you in here."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:35.67,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,You should get going. I'll handle things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:38.39,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I owe you one, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.14,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.65,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri turned violent?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.11,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Is that why her memory was erased?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:00.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Or maybe she's just pretending,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:02.41,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and she really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.43,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.14,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,My name is Yasuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:26.35,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,I was head of Yamasaki Factory's research and development department.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:27.85,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,For Humanoids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.86,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,I apologize for disturbing your plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.65,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,but could I invite you for a little chat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.86,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,This rain just won't let up, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.78,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,You must have it rough with that leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:47.20,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Believe me, I understand. I'm the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:50.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Skip the small talk. Just get to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Was Atri the one who got violent at that school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:17.23,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I trust you recognize that string.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.57,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri's log...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:25.66,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,YHN-04B-009.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.91,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,That is that unit's official serial number.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.58,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The fourth generation was made to keep written logs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:36.75,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,in an effort to pursue more human methods
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.26,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,of building memories and learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:43.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,"Today, I met my first master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.35,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Her name is-"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.31,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.60,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,A penny for your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:58.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No... This can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:10.12,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,To create a copy of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.37,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Is that the culmination of human scientific progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:16.42,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,or is it an inviolable taboo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:20.63,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,That was the question Professor Konishi sought to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.38,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Konishi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:28.43,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,My mentor. The one who created the Humanoids.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:30.56,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The rampage at the school
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:33.27,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,ended Professor Konishi's career--and eventually, life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:39.27,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,It is my duty to recover that incomplete model
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.36,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,and dispose of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:46.74,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,I consider it the bare minimum goodwill I can show the world and the Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:51.04,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Can I trust you to cooperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.79,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,There is only one unit left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:01.55,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Once I dispose of that unit, my work will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.51,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,I understand how you must feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.80,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The fourth generation was impeccably made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:10.68,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,They comprehend human emotion algorithms
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:14.73,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,well enough to uphold the illusion that they possess genuine emotions themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:19.23,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,But they do not {\i1}actually{\i0} have hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:23.61,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Surely you have realized this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:26.99,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Your feelings, no matter how strong, will never reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.83,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,I assure you that the only heart to break
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.79,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,will be your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:42.09,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I... need some time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.49,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You're acting different today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.70,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I am following your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:19.83,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,If I told you to act like you always do, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.92,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I will follow orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:25.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's an order, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Act like you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.55,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Nat suki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:34.60,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. Come to think of it, I haven't had anything to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.69,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Oh, we can't have that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:47.24,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Wait right there! I'll heat up Mom's Cooking, Part Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Curry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:51.45,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,H-How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.66,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Curry is a classic day-after-nikujaga meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,They use the same ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:00.71,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Really? Your deductive prowess astounds me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.25,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Stop pretending you have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.86,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Dinner is served.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.13,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Does it taste good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:52.13,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,If I said yes, would it make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:54.76,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.80,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.31,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be {\i1}happy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:00.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You'd just make a log in your AI saying you made the right choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.15,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.90,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I am a Humanoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.70,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:19.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Of course you wouldn't know how to react to my nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:20.12,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.04,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:27.09,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I want to be alone. Don't follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:49.40,Default,Subordinate A,0,0,0,,What's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:56.61,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,The low-pressure system's wind speeds are still increasing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:58.58,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,so people will need to be very careful out in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:03.71,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,We can expect heavy winds around coastal areas, so ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:23.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm out at sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.27,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:38.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.37,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:15.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Ririka came and said that the school is in danger, so I have gone with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:18.99,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:20.82,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:40.59,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah, that's how it is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:43.56,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Why didn't I understand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:44.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,something so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:49.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:51.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.62,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,Hana-chan-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:06.12,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,How could you take some little kids hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.04,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,By all means, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:11.29,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,They will be free to go just as soon as that unit arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:15.96,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid. It won't be much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:19.05,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Ririka went to go get Atri-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:21.84,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Yeah. They should be here any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:30.35,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,And here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.19,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Where is your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:36.52,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Where's Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:38.90,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,That's the thing! I couldn't find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.49,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Natsu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.11,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Well, no matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:44.99,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:57.38,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.59,Default,Toru and Miyo,0,0,0,,Hana-chan-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:05.60,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,There, there. It's okay. Everything's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:09.18,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with Atri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:20.65,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Atri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:28.20,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Oh, the show's just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:32.16,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Burn the sight into your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.50,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Witness just how dangerous this Humanoid is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.80,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Atri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.30,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You mother-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.47,Default,Subordinate,0,0,0,,Shut up and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.48,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:58.06,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,You attack a school, disgrace the Professor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:00.19,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,and even escape on top of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:04.49,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,How much suffering must you cause before you're satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.95,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Were you that determined to see your own creator,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:14.08,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,see the Professor's life fall apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.01,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Atri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:31.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Fuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:48.07,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:51.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I need to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:53.08,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Need to go be with...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:58.08,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I need to go be with that bootleg LLM!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:01.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She's cheeky, for a robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:06.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She keeps bragging about her high specs right before screwing up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:15.39,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She's annoying, and she's too meddlesome for her own good...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:19.60,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She's got a heart more beautiful than any human's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:23.19,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And she's my piece-of-crap Humanoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:29.99,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,You defective {\i1}wretch{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:32.58,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,If it weren't for you, the Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:35.08,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The Professor! The Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:37.54,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:45.76,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,If it weren't for you and what you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:55.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:22:57.18,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:22:59.77,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,You've had your fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:02.65,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,What? Surely you jest!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:07.15,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,This is a {\i1}Humanoid{\i0}. This is nothing to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:10.49,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:12.16,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:17.70,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,If there's one thing you're good at, it's inspiring empathy in humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:20.67,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Really, you terrify me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.67,0:23:22.46,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,You hopeless,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:24.71,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,damnable monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:27.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:37.35,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
